entries.text: Hello! How can I help you today?
Hi, I need to replace my lost gold card. Can you send it to the...
I understand that you need to replace your Gold card. Can you please confirm the address you would like the replacement card sent to? Would you like it sent to the address on file or a new address?
Thank you. I'll wait for the confirmation.
Could you please confirm the address where you'd like the replacement Gold card to be sent? Would you like it sent to the address we have on file, or to a new address?
Great, I'll keep an eye out for it. Thank you for your help.

Your request to replace the lost Gold card has been processed, and it will be sent to the address we have on file. Thank you for your patience, and if you need further assistance, feel free to ask. Have a great day!
You're welcome. Have a nice day.
